  <official_title>Controlled Release of Oxycodone 10 mg In Pre-Medication For The Post Operative Analgesia In Elective Laparoscopic Bilateral Inguinal Hernia And Elective Laparoscopic Cholecystectomy : Prospective Double Blind, Randomized, Placebo-Controlled Study</official_title>
